            <br><P CLASS="post">
              Hello everyone, we are getting ready to put together another major list of updates and new features to add and I wanted to see if any of you have some more ideas?<br><br>Here are some of the updates we have for our new list, if you have anymore you would like to see please reply to this thread!<br><br>1. A full working gallery, our current studio is not hacking it.<br><br>2. Updates to some auction images<br><br>3. Auctions over 2 months old will be removed to help increase the speed of the database<br><br>4. Sellers currently get 3 emails for each auction, this will be consolidated to 1 email<br><br>5. Allow numbers and emails to be shown in the message center as well as adding a reply button<br><br>6. Verification system for buyers and sellers<br><br>7. A system to allow users to see who they have not left feedback for, allowing them to leave it if they want.<br><br>Please feel free to add any suggestions you have.<br><br><br>Thank You<br>Shane aka Lux
